      <title>中国Z-​​10攻击直升机首次海外亮相，但出口前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-z-10-attack-helicopter-makes-foreign-debut-export-outlook-uncertain-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国航空工业集团公司在新加坡航展上首次在国外展示了Z-10攻击直升机，这是今年没有俄罗斯国防公司参加的唯一一次非西方设计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-z-10-attack-helicopter-makes-foreign-debut-export-outlook-uncertain-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 01:23:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国维持利率稳定，投资者关注转向时机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-holds-rates-steady-investors-eye-timing-pivot-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行周四将利率维持在 15 年来的高位，有迹象表明经济疲软正在减缓通胀，投资者将注意力集中在行长李昌镛 (Rhee Chang-yong) 关于今年晚些时候政策转向时机的评论上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-holds-rates-steady-investors-eye-timing-pivot-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 01:00:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
